== About me
I am a first year PhD student in [https://www.ecse.rpi.edu Electrical, Computer, and System Engineering Department] at [http://https://www.rpi.edu Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute], working under the supervision of [https://www.ecse.rpi.edu/~tajer Prof. Ali Tajer]. Before that, I graduated from University of Science and Technology of China.\n
